flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New model program kickoff or scheduled launch-planning cycle (stage-gate approval to set initial production volumes).]
  A --> N1[Stream: STREAMS + DDM/Crawlers - Consolidate demand history, variant master, capacity and market feeds into subject area]
  N1 --> N2[Agent: Cortex Auto Forecast + Agent Team - Generate baseline and probabilistic variant-level forecasts and analog-based new-model signals]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: Remote Functions (scenario simulation) + Process Builder (Data Science) - Simulate launch volume & ramp scenarios and score impacts on COGS, revenue, inventory and capacity]
  N3 --> N4{PB: Process Builder (IF) + CWB Lifecycle - Rank top-N launch profiles and route recommendations for human-in-the-loop review}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Remote Functions (ERP writeback) + Notification - Write approved production plan to SAP and notify planning/manufacturing stakeholders]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Cortex Monitoring + Process Builder (Wait/Asynchronous) - Monitor launch performance, update forecasts, and adjust ramps as evidence accrues]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Aligned production launch plan committed to ERP reducing over/under production risk, improved revenue capture from demand-aligned supply, lower working capital tied to launch inventory, and demonstrable COGS optimization across ramp profiles.]
  N4 -->|Market intelligence indicates high un...| B1[Agent Team launches focused data collection (external feeds, dealer outreach) and generates wider scenario bands; decision deferred to next planning cycle or flagged for senior review.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Decision delayed with expanded uncertainty bands; human reviewer action required to proceed or postpone launch commitments.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Plant capacity or critical supplier c...| B2[Process Builder invokes remediation flow: propose alternative lower ramp, phased production across plants, or supplier escalation via Action Item.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Adjusted launch profile that fits constraints or a high-priority mitigation plan is created; reduced risk of infeasible commitments.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|Forecast accuracy or model confidence...| B3[Escalate to manual planning via CWB Lifecycle with enriched scenario inputs and require explicit override to execute writeback.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Human-approved conservative plan or additional validation steps before ERP commit, preventing overcommitment on low-confidence forecasts.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]